<p>Wild Nights<br />
By Emily Dickinson</p>

<p>Wild Nights - Wild Nights<br />
Were I with thee<br />
Wild Nights should be<br />
Our luxury!</p>

<p>Futile - the winds -<br />
To the heart in port -<br />
Done with the compass -<br />
Done with the chart!</p>

<p>Rowing in Eden -<br />
Ah, the sea!<br />
Might I but moor Tonight -<br />
In Thee!</p>

